-17T00:23:42.000Z","msg":"搵唔到source<br />\n想知大家開口埋口話一萬億既source邊度黎<br />\n有既我收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T01:17:50.000Z","msg":"官方只係五千億，一萬億係用黎老作增加宣傳效果，雖然都有可能超支"},{"pid":"270ca3f9ee1aa9c3049282f181eb217a5702861d","tid":865212,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T01:22:04.000Z","msg":"Ok 淨係起個島 交通配套基建超支都唔洗理"},{"pid":"8c06ef2796f199b1afa2bd08ea709843ffd8b2bb","tid":865212,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T01:50:53.000Z","msg":"填海只係藉口 揼水俾阿爺維穩先真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}